data.description: *$5,000 Bonus-SEE AGENT ONLY REMARKS* GORGEOUS home on 1.95 acres! Shaker style, vinyl siding. Covered front and back porches, additional concrete patio. and 2 storage bldgs + garden beds. Extra, paved parking & 2 car, attached garage with workspace and storage closet. 22 SOLAR PANELS atop the home! This home has potential for independent, additional family living & PASSIVE INCOME. Upper level living space (only accessible from outside & not included in total sq ft - BONUS) has a full bath, living rm w/pony wall separating space into a bdrm. Main level back porch (accessible by living rm & primary bd), stunning custom kitchen, stainless steel appliances, huge island, granite countertops, 3 bdrm, 2 ba (primary has large shower), laundry rm, vaulted ceilings & lots of windows for amazing natural light. Basement is an additional, separate living space with full kitchen, full bath, den, 2 rooms that can be used as bdrms & patio space.  Stairs from main level to basement have a lift chair.
